section(class="template-wrapper self_7")
    aside(class="template-asideLeft o-aside-Item")
    |
    |
    div(class="template-section m-a")
        section(class="template-content")
            div(class="row-flex align-items-center")
                h5(class="mb35 row") Choose the best answer for the following questions:
                div(class="col xs12 lg4 ta-c")
                    
                    img(src="unit_3/module_10/assets/images/col_3.png", alt="act_2" class="u-responsive-img m-a")


                div(class="col xs12 sm6 lg4 ta-l ")
                    div
                        h6 #[span(class="u-textColor_4"): strong 1. ] What is an appropriate name for the text?
                        p
                            input(id="inputRadio_1" type='radio', class="c-inputRadio" name='selInputRadio_1' value="1")
                            label(class="c-Checkbox" for='inputRadio_1' ng-click="txtcaptura_a='told'"): span The laws of Colombia. 
                        p
                            input(id="inputRadio_2" type='radio', class="c-inputRadio" name='selInputRadio_1' value="2")
                            label(class="c-Checkbox" for='inputRadio_2' ng-click="txtcaptura_a='told'"): span  Colombian Customs regulation. 
                        p
                            input(id="inputRadio_3" type='radio', class="c-inputRadio" name='selInputRadio_1' value="3")
                            label(class="c-Checkbox" for='inputRadio_3' ng-click="txtcaptura_a='told'"): span  Custom agents.

                    div
                        h6 #[span(class="u-textColor_4"): strong 2. ] Upon arrival at El Dorado International Airport, all foreign passengers must have a...
                        p
                            input(id="inputRadio_4" type='radio', class="c-inputRadio" name='selInputRadio_2' value="1")
                            label(class="c-Checkbox" for='inputRadio_4' ng-click="txtcaptura_a='told'"): span Passport. 
                        p
                            input(id="inputRadio_5" type='radio', class="c-inputRadio" name='selInputRadio_2' value="2")
                            label(class="c-Checkbox" for='inputRadio_5' ng-click="txtcaptura_a='told'"): span  Visa.
                        p
                            input(id="inputRadio_6" type='radio', class="c-inputRadio" name='selInputRadio_2' value="3")
                            label(class="c-Checkbox" for='inputRadio_6' ng-click="txtcaptura_a='told'"): span  money to pay the embarkation tax.

                    div
                        h6 #[span(class="u-textColor_4"): strong 3. ]  If I left my bag in the airport door, where can I go to reclaim it?
                        p
                            input(id="inputRadio_7" type='radio', class="c-inputRadio" name='selInputRadio_3' value="1")
                            label(class="c-Checkbox" for='inputRadio_7' ng-click="txtcaptura_a='told'"): span In the same spot. 
                        p
                            input(id="inputRadio_8" type='radio', class="c-inputRadio" name='selInputRadio_3' value="2")
                            label(class="c-Checkbox" for='inputRadio_8' ng-click="txtcaptura_a='told'"): span  In the baggage claim.
                        p
                            input(id="inputRadio_9" type='radio', class="c-inputRadio" name='selInputRadio_3' value="3")
                            label(class="c-Checkbox" for='inputRadio_9' ng-click="txtcaptura_a='told'"): span You cannot claim it.

                div(class="col xs12 sm6 lg4 ta-l  ")
                    div
                        h6 #[span(class="u-textColor_4"): strong 4. ] If I have a bullet in my pocket what will happen to me at customs in El Dorado International Airport?
                        p
                            input(id="inputRadio_10" type='radio', class="c-inputRadio" name='selInputRadio_4' value="1")
                            label(class="c-Checkbox" for='inputRadio_10' ng-click="txtcaptura_a='told'"): span It will be taken from me and I will Board the flight.
                        p
                            input(id="inputRadio_11" type='radio', class="c-inputRadio" name='selInputRadio_4' value="2")
                            label(class="c-Checkbox" for='inputRadio_11' ng-click="txtcaptura_a='told'"): span I will be searched, questioned and possible arrested.  
                        p
                            input(id="inputRadio_12" type='radio', class="c-inputRadio" name='selInputRadio_4' value="3")
                            label(class="c-Checkbox" for='inputRadio_12' ng-click="txtcaptura_a='told'"): span My bags will be searched and I will be allowed on the flight. 

                    div
                        h6 #[span(class="u-textColor_4"): strong 5. ] What will happen if I have U.S.$5,000 in my pocket and U.S. $5,001 in my luggage?
                        p
                            input(id="inputRadio_13" type='radio', class="c-inputRadio" name='selInputRadio_5' value="1")
                            label(class="c-Checkbox" for='inputRadio_13' ng-click="txtcaptura_a='told'"): span It ok because you only have U.S. $5,000 in my pocket. 
                        p
                            input(id="inputRadio_14" type='radio', class="c-inputRadio" name='selInputRadio_5' value="2")
                            label(class="c-Checkbox" for='inputRadio_14' ng-click="txtcaptura_a='told'"): span The extra U.S.$1.00 will be taken away.
                        p
                            input(id="inputRadio_15" type='radio', class="c-inputRadio" name='selInputRadio_5' value="3")
                            label(class="c-Checkbox" for='inputRadio_15' ng-click="txtcaptura_a='told'"): span The entire amount will be confiscated and you will be questioned.
                        







